HEADWORD: Chacma
<hw>Chac"ma</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Native
name.]</ety> <def>A large species of African baboon (<spn>Cynocephalus
porcarius</spn>); -- called also <altname>ursine baboon</altname>.
<note>[See <xex>Illust.</xex> of <er>Baboon</er>.]</note></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

